Package: spAgroClimate
Title: Agroclimatic variables and spatial distribution
Version: 0.0.0.9
Authors@R: 
    person("Guillermo S.", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package provides a set of functions to calculate agroclimatic variables and their spatial distribution. It aims to help agricultural researchers and practitioners to analyze and model agroclimatic data.
Depends:
    raster, sp, ggplot2, lubridate, reshape2, pbapply, terra
